title: A Controversial Decision in Oregon Could Cost Democrats the House
description:
Progressive Jamie McLeod-Skinner trails by 2 points in a race the national Democratic super PACs preemptively deemed unwinnable. She’s not the only one.

title: Rupert Murdoch Is Having the Same Problem Dr. Frankenstein Once Faced With His Monster
